## Python Settings

```shell
pip install ipython, pep8, pytest, rope, jedi
```

## 配置 vscode 为 git 编辑器

`git config --global core.editor "code --wait"`

## Problems

```yaml
"Extension host terminated execptedly": "新装的插件不兼容，卸载掉即可"
```
